6 December 2013Media are invited to a joint technical media briefing hosted by Government Communication and Information System (GCIS) and the SABC on the media arrangements of the state funeral of President Mandela. The details are as follows: Date: Saturday, 7 December 2013 Time: 9h00 Venue: SABC Studios, Auckland ParkGovernment has also created a dedicated website where all announcements and media related information is uploaded daily: www.mandela.gov.za. Enquiries: Phumla Williams, Acting Government Spokesperson 083 501 0139 Issued by Government Communication and Information System(GCIS)